> > > I think Wolfgang has discussed this elsewhere
> > > (https://www.metafor-project.org/doku.php/analyses:konstantopoulos2011).
> > > In short, ~ 1 | Study/Time is a reparametrization of ~Time|Study,
> > > struct = "CS".
> > >
> > > Best,
> > > Reza
