> > > across the studies, you can create a 'condition' variable to
> > > distinguish between the control and the treatments' SMCCs (yi) in each
> > > study over the intervals you have defined:
> > >
> > > study condition  yi  interval_id id
> > > 1     T1        .1   0           1
> > > 1     T1        .3   1           2
> > > 1     T2        .7   0           3
> > > 1     T2        .2   1           4
> > > 1     C         .4   0           5
> > > 1     C         .5   1           6
> > > 2     T2        .6   0           7
> > > 2     C         .9   1           8
