>> Borenstein, M., Higgins, J. P., Hedges, L. V., & Rothstein, H. R. (2017).
>> Basics of meta?analysis: I2 is not an absolute measure of heterogeneity. *Research
>> synthesis methods*, *8*(1), 5-18.
